walk around the dresser

Place the tissue box  on the toilet
anns.task_desc: Take the tissue box in the dresser Place the tissue box  on the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the dresser to your left.
Pick up tissue box from the desk.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the toilet.
Place tissue box on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Moving tissue box from one location to another.

high_descs: Turn right, move forward towards the dresser.
Take the tissue box from the dresser.
Turn left, take right, leave the room, take right, move, take left enter into toilet.
Look around the toilet, put the tissue box on the toilet water tank.
anns.task_desc: To put the tissue box on the toilet water tank.
